sources.description:
Did he finally get his big break, or will they break him?
A trio of hapless bounty hunters are recruited by a shady bail bondsman to try to keep a witness in drug trial alive to testify.

Director & Writer: Max Kleven
Casting: David Hasselhoff, Linda Blair, Tony Brubaker
Genres: Action, Comedy, Crime, Thriller
